{"type": "article", "id": 63631, "title": "Louis Vuitton 开通小红书账号，以及，深圳品牌 ROARINGWILD 指海澜之家抄袭 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2019-05-09T01:28:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}, {"id": 44846, "name": "Asics"}, {"id": 10733, "name": "i-D"}, {"id": 58459, "name": "ROARINGWILD"}, {"id": 17291, "name": "海澜之家"}, {"id": 54947, "name": "CELINE"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190509090000We2srnm4Xt7CHFMh.JPG", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/fossil-stock-rallies-after-companys-q1-sales-in-china-india-grow-2019-05-08\" rel=\"nofollow\">美国手表及配饰品牌 Fossil 第一季度亏损收窄</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 截至 3 月 31 日的第一季度内，Fossil 销售额同比下跌 18% 至 4.65 亿美元，亏损从去年同期的 4830 万美元收窄至 1220 万美元。中国及印度市场均取得了两位数增长，助推亚洲市场销售额保持稳健，而美国市场则继续下滑。该公司预计第二季度销售额跌幅将达到 10% 至 16%，全年跌幅则将在 7% 至 12 % 之间。消息发布后，Fossil 股价于周三上涨了 11%。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Asics-has-tough-Q1-but-sees-areas-of-strength,1096890.html#.XNN3VdMzbOQ\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本运动品牌 Asics 第一季度大中华区销售额下滑 26%</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Asics 第一季度销售额下跌 5.7% 至 987 亿日元（约 60.7 亿元人民币），营业利润下跌 27.6% 至 61.8 亿日元，净利润下跌 17.9% 至 43.6 亿日元。从市场看，日本及北美销售额分别增长 0.4% 和 4.2%，欧洲及大中华区则分别下滑 14% 及 26.1%。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Alastair-McKimm-is-Global-Editor-In-Chief-of-i-D,1096717.html#.XNN5TNMzbOQ\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vice Media 任 Alastair McKimm 为 i-D 杂志全球主编</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Alastair McKimm 将于 6 月上任。他于 20 年前进入 i-D 工作，当时担任 Edward Enninful（现为英国版 Vogue 主编）的助手，并于 2013 年升任时装总监。i-D 杂志将于明年庆祝成立 40 周年。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/louis-vuitton-debuts-on-chinas-xiaohongshu-1203126591/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Louis Vuitton 开通小红书官方账号</a>。</strong></p><p>Louis Vuitton 也是首个进驻该平台的奢侈品牌。根据小红书对外公布的数据，该平台目前共有超过 2 亿用户，其中 60% 来自一二线城市，70% 为 90 后或更年轻的群体，明年预计营收将翻倍至 29 亿美元。据 WWD 报道，还会有更多奢侈品牌将入驻该平台。</p><p>目前 Louis Vuitton 的账号一共发布了一条视频和 6 张图片，已有 1 万粉丝及 1.9 万个赞。视频内容为时尚博主“包先生”荐包，图片中出现的人物则包括迪丽热巴、范丞丞、焦俊艳等明星以及小红书博主陈白羊。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509075036hiHxMzvtdPYKVrTS.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"3.989333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>由六名在校大学生于 2010 年创立的深圳品牌 ROARINGWILD 昨日在官方公众号<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/lYrD79G9ITDGkwNCJSnlnQ\" rel=\"nofollow\">发布视频及图文</a>，指<strong>海澜之家旗下新潮牌黑鲸 HLAJEANS 抄袭 ROARINGWILD 2018 年春夏款式</strong>。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905090733321InlBZoGaRefwgu7.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.217333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905090733455AQK1Gpg3jhRrFLw.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.564000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905090734103VCrsMKO1kf5Rl6m.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.428704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509073403j9R0s62LzvO75fob.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.428704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509073403rtX0HGfIqgF6kOLj.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.428704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/fashion/article/44356/1/hedi-slimane-celine-fw19-collection-campaign-shitkid-video-paris\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hedi Slimane 为 CELINE 拍摄的第二组广告大片出炉。</a></strong></p><p>2018 年秋冬大片仍然以 Hedi Slimane 标志性的黑白配色为主。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509080953qFOcmk3nyxbwDraV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509080953rh2FBLAOWJV1ft9y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509080954AUPQ7hTpVqd29zj3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509080954CvIBDkLgfeE7VQiY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509080954176RzNY5Q3vAbhXk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509080955NAvompy9rfk41nwY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509080955j8HN0tnE3qcMVrw5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509080955wjiXaRhrtOZuIknA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509080956jLyPqQnUsiw4SCZK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905090809566wpm8yGuALUYTcVt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019050908095661bQTymiJKAtwERF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509080956Szl5e2bvUu6j8WcZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509080957xL6qjUsltZC824cf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509080957e9MiYVGhrtPLzsQb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509080957cWz8idqtZvwP1SAx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2019/5/stussy-summer-2019-collection-editorial-release\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Stüssy 发布 2019 夏季系列 Lookbook</a></strong>，由长期与&nbsp;《Buffalo》杂志合作的摄影师 Mark Lebon 拍摄。</p><p>该系列将于 5 月 10 日在&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.stussy.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stüssy</a>&nbsp;官网、Chapter 门店以及 Dover Street Market&nbsp;伦敦及洛杉矶门店。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509071642rM3n9aRzKkfe0HuC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509071708MU3NHWljTLz2aGY0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905090716425AgbjcnY9MEifz0V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509071643axTkd9lEIrpMsFh3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509071643rYTESmu1BxMZP4Iq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509071644VXthr3eSINysxqpj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/mark-lim-nicotine-magazine-photography-080519\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>Nicotine magazine</em>&nbsp;造型特辑。</a></strong></p><p>摄影 Mark Lim，造型 Lilia Toncheva O’Rourke，艺术 Lizzy Oppenheimer。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905090822245HsWkKFNzv8uQTa0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.324586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019050908222438Rim0pWshGCPJYa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.324586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190509082223KQuA2xo9WdRq1lZj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.324586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;